It seems to me that there’s more to Ace Magashule and crew’s fact-finding and/or mediation mission to Zimbabwe than meets the eye. It seems the ANC is primarily there to share notes with the ruling Zanu-PF on the longevity of liberation movements that are way past their sell-by dates. Luyanda Marlon KamaKwadwesi The FM welcomes concise letters from readers. They can be sent to fmmail@fm.co.za